data.description: Up to $20,000 flex cash available from Ameritex, now is the time to get into a new construction home! This flex cash can be used to buy down the interest rate or used toward covering closing costs. Wow! What an offer on this beautiful new duplex featuring 6 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms total, plus modern amenities throughout. You'll fall in love with the open concept family room that is perfect for gathering with friends and family! This space provides a seamless dining and entertaining experience. The energy-efficient features and appliances in this home are proven to keep utility costs down. This new construction home is a treasured find in this Monterey High School Neighborhood. Don't miss the chance to take advantage of this 6% flex cash making your dream of homeownership a reality. Make this your home sweet home today!
